msg: On the 'move-tracking-2' branch: Remove a special case from the editor3
(svn_editor3_alter): A null payload parameter no longer means "no change":
it means this is a subbranch-root element.
(editor3_alter): No longer fetch the old payload if the parameter is null.
(do_move): Update the call to svn_editor3_alter: instead of passing null
to avoid changing the payload, fetch and pass the old payload.
